8
00:00:24,680 --> 00:00:25,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Die Reisetomate.</font>

9
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:26,920
<font color=#00FFFF>Stierstirn.</font>

10
00:00:26,920 --> 00:00:28,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Tigerella.</font>

11
00:00:28,040 --> 00:00:29,080
<font color=#00FFFF>Pink Tiger.</font>

12
00:00:29,080 --> 00:00:30,840
